","tid":1005993,"uid":99473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"唔洗三個月啦<br />\n下兩星期佢IG已經拖住第二個隻手"},{"pid":"7313d70da0c0404c8ed1328192f638e50021462a","tid":1005993,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b11ff26e347d60df3c3e558909d0cadc38dd641d","tid":1005993,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T17:37:17.000Z","msg":"不如你查下上進嘅定義先，唔係字典到查，係社會"},{"pid":"3d22b07aa63add7dc6aeaf75e13991f04a301667","tid":1005993,"uid":13302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad65a824701130eda29f8f321d4b03ef882312bc","tid":1005993,"uid":149991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45c0e86a4b6e009c9c0ca312b3215c95fdc3dd40","tid":1005993,"uid":13302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n共勉之"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"多謝你 真係好多謝<br />\n見到呢句 眼淚忍唔住咁流<br />\n你都有你嘅故事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T01:22:20.000Z","msg":"自己嘅故事唔多請啦<br />\n只可以講明白你而家嘅處境"},{"pid":"fdd6fcc7acc8db7d59f4e690fb5af4c7bc2b481b","tid":1005993,"uid":229408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T01:33:48.000Z","msg":"最愛那一個<br />\n一般 沒有結果"},{"pid":"f51b929b9557025adde8c263f46632b00b8ff871","tid":1005993,"uid":154442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:05:56.000Z","msg":"講多少少點懶點唔上進得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n有時唔一定真係呢樣<br />\n<br />\n可以係條女厭咗而出面又有新仔approach<br />\n<br />\n幾年前我都一樣係咁， 諗返其實真係條女臭雞"},{"pid":"a758f4f1c5635b6eac897fec38a7af20d466ce43","tid":1005993,"uid":205534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:11:59.000Z","msg":"要把握呢個所謂嘅機會呀<br />\n好多人連改變嘅機會都無<br />\n話散就散<br />\n我唔講事實去打擊樓主<br />\n總之加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicke